PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE MANITOBA FISHERY REGULATIONS, 1987 by prohibiting the transport, possession or release into any waters of live specimens of the species listed in Schedule IX to the MFR as part of a precautionary approach intended to proactively protect Manitoba's aquatic ecosystems.
